## Store memories for

- P4/P5 tuning outcomes and winning parameter sets
- Guardian drift debounce behavior and VD latency quirks
- Deploy path issues (`01spacecalibrator` vs stale DLL)
- IPC race fixes and version bump rationale

Use tags like `calibration`, `guardian`, `quest-slam`, `p4-tuning`, `deploy`, `ipc`.

## Build notes

- CMake/MSVC Windows project; build output under `bin/`
- Bump `src/common/Version.h` when IPC or driver protocol changes
- Do not commit personal `profiles/p4-*.json` or log artifacts